
MONSTERS:

1. Rabbit- Level 3
2. Chicken- 3 @ Level 3
3. Rooster- Level 4
4. Cat- Level 4
5. Dog- Level 4
6. Farmer- Level 7
7. Wife- Level 6
8. Son- Level 6

MONSTER LOCATION:

1. The rabbit is located in /players/jara/area1/farm1/room/field1.c
   to field4.c  It will wander randomly between these four rooms.
2. The chickens are located in /players/jara/area1/farm1/room/hutch.c
   There are a total of 3 chickens.
3. The rooster is located in /players/jara/area1/farm1/room/hutch.c
4. The cat is located in /players/jara/area1/farm1/room/path1.c to
   path8.c  It will wander randomly between these 8 rooms.
5. The dog is located in /players/jara/area1/farm1/room/barn2.c
6. The farmer is located in /players/jara/area1/farm1/room/house3.c
7. The wife is located in /players/jara/area1/farm1/room/house2.c
8. The son is located in /players/jara/area1/farm1/room/house4.c

THEME:

The small farm is just outside the city, to the southwest. It is a newbie
area with a farm family, a field of corn and some other farm-related rooms/
items/objects. 

MAP:

A map is located in /players/jara/area1/farm1/misc/MAP

